doctype html
html
  body
    h3 SoCraTes Registration Confirmation
    p.
      Hello #{member.displayName()},
    p Congratulations! You are now registered for the SoCraTes Conference 2015.
    p
      | You have booked a #{' '} 
      b #{bookingdetails.room}
      | #{' '} for #{' '}
      b #{bookingdetails.nights}
      | #{' '} nights until #{' '}
      b #{bookingdetails.until}
      | .
    p As soon as we receive your payment we will send you a payment confirmation email.
    p You can review and modify your registration data and access the payment information at #{' '}
      a(href='#{url}/members/edit') #{url}/members/edit

    p You can review your booking information at #{' '}
      a(href='#{url}/registration') #{url}/registration

    p If you have questions, need help or want to give feedback, just reply to this e-mail.
